            <title>[SUREFIRE-548] System properties not inherited</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-548</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
