                            <comment id="14454768" author="krosenvold" created="Fri, 21 Jan 2011 16:54:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Treated as documentation issue, docs updated in r1062064,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  To inherit the &quot;systemProperties&quot; collection from the parent configuration,&lt;br/&gt;
  you will need to specify combine.children=&quot;append&quot; on the systemProperties node in the child pom:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  &amp;lt;systemProperties combine.children=&quot;append&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;...&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/systemProperties&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
